{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Passkey autofill makes it easy for your users to use Passkeys. If the user already has a passkey on their device they will be able to select it from the keyboard autofill as soon as the focus the identifier input."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"autofill"}]},{"anchor":"How-to-enable","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"How to enable"},{"anchor":"Setup-Your-Input","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Setup Your Input"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You will need to set the textContentType of your identifier input to be “username”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can set this in interface builder, or in code:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you have a reference in your controller to identifierField:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["identifierField.textContentType = \"username\" "]},{"anchor":"Start-the-Autofill-Service","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Start the Autofill Service"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"”””"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You will need to start the autofill service as early in the process as you can on the View that is rendering your identifier field."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For example when a view appears:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    override func viewDidAppear(_ animated: Bool) {","        guard let window = self.view.window else { fatalError(\"The view was not in the app's view hierarchy!\") }","        DispatchQueue.main.asyncAfter(deadline: .now() + 1) {","            Task {","                try await PassageAuth.beginAutoFill(anchor: window, onSuccess: self.onAutofillSuccess, onError: self.onAutofillError, onCancel: nil)","            }","        }","        \/\/ other code","    }"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You will need to pass onSuccess, onError, and onCancel methods to handle autofill callbacks, all three are optional but it is recommended you handle onSuccess and OnError at a minimum. So you can respond to the results if they select the passkey to autofill."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["func onAutofillSuccess(authResult: AuthResult) {","    if let token = authResult.auth_token {","        DispatchQueue.main.async {","            self.pushWelcomeViewController(token: token)","        }","    }","}"]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["func onAutofillError(error: Error) {","    DispatchQueue.main.async {","        self.displayError(message: \"Error logging in with autofill\")","    }","}    "]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/passage\/guide_passkeyautofill"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Passage\/documentation\/Passage\/Guide_PasskeyAutofill","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Enable Passkey autofill to make it easier for your users to login with Passkeys."}],"kind":"article","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","title":"Guide PasskeyAutofill","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"Passage"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Passage\/documentation\/Passage"]]},"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Guides","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Passage\/documentation\/Passage\/Guide_PassageFramework","doc:\/\/Passage\/documentation\/Passage\/Guide_Registration","doc:\/\/Passage\/documentation\/Passage\/Guide_Login","doc:\/\/Passage\/documentation\/Passage\/Guide_SessionManagement"],"generated":true}],"references":{"doc://Passage/documentation/Passage":{"role":"collection","title":"Passage","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Use Passage to add exclusively Passwordless authentication to your iOS Application."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Passage\/documentation\/Passage","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/passage"},"doc://Passage/documentation/Passage/Guide_SessionManagement":{"role":"article","title":"Session Management","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This guide provides an overview of how session management is handled using Passage and how to use passage-ios to handle refresh tokens."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Passage\/documentation\/Passage\/Guide_SessionManagement","kind":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/passage\/guide_sessionmanagement"},"doc://Passage/documentation/Passage/Guide_PassageFramework":{"role":"article","title":"Getting Started","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This guide provides a high level view of the passage-ios framework and how to get started with it."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Passage\/documentation\/Passage\/Guide_PassageFramework","kind":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/passage\/guide_passageframework"},"doc://Passage/documentation/Passage/Guide_Registration":{"role":"article","title":"User Registration","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This guide will explain how to register new users with the passage-ios framework."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Passage\/documentation\/Passage\/Guide_Registration","kind":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/passage\/guide_registration"},"doc://Passage/documentation/Passage/Guide_Login":{"role":"article","title":"Login","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This guide will explain how to log in users with the passage-ios framework."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Passage\/documentation\/Passage\/Guide_Login","kind":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/passage\/guide_login"},"autofill":{"alt":"Passkey Autofill","type":"image","identifier":"autofill","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/autofill.gif","traits":["1x","light"]}]}}}